Name: Seafarer's Hearth
Description: Harness the power of the sea, reducing the cooldown of your Hearthstone by ${$a1658}% when used in Kul Tiras and Zandalar.

Name: Swift Landing
Description: Capture the momentum from your recent flight path, increasing your mounted movement speed by ${$a1661}% for ${$a1662} minutes upon landing.

Name: Upgraded Troop Barracks
Description: Construct a larger barracks for your army, increasing the maximum number of troops you can house by ${$a1664}.

Name: Troop Portal Network
Description: Open a portal for transportation of troops from Orgrimmar, allowing troops to be recruited instantly.

Name: Local Transportation

Name: Step of Faith
Description:
Allows travel to Elysian Hold, Hero's Rest, Aspirant's Rest, and the Temple of Courage.

After arriving at a location cast Unburden, greatly increasing movement speed, and propelling you forward.

Name: Leap of Power
Description:
Allows travel to Sagehaven, the Temple of Purity, and the Seat of Eternal Hymns.

Unburden duration increased by 100%.

Your Summon Steward ability can now create an Elysian Beacon, granting you access to the network in the field.

Name: Eternal Paths
Description:
Allows travel to the Temple of Humility and Exaltation Rise.

Unburden additionally reduces the radius at which enemies will detect you while active.

Your steward's Elysian Beacon can now be used by party members.

Name: Flowing Tendrils
Description: Allows you to channel anima to Purity's Pinnacle and the Temple of Courage, granting access to a special treasure and an enemy champion.

Name: Streaming Threads
Description: Allows you to channel anima to the Temple of Humility and the Eternal Forge, granting access to a new World Quest and new Daily Quests.

Name: Flowing Power
Description: Allows you to channel anima to the Eonian Archives and the Citadel of Loyalty, granting access to Kyrian enhancements and a powerful enemy champion.

Description: Unlocks access to the Sanctum's first two anima diversion locations.

Name: First Planting
Description: Access to the Queen's Conservatory, where you will learn to restore the souls of lost gods to life.

Name: Initial Growth
Description: Unlocks access to catalyst plots, and activates an additional wildseed. Conservator Aoni will now offer daily catalyst quests.

Name: Nurtured Souls
Description: Activates additional wildseed and catalyst plots to expand your growing potential.

Name: Flourishing Beds
Description: Activates additional wildseed and catalyst plots. Opens access to a wildseed that has three possible catalyst connections.

Name: Final Forms
Description: Activates the final wildseed plot that has access to four possible catalyst links.

Name: First Steps
Description: Unlocks the sacred trial of the Path of Ascension, facilitating the capture of six Shadowlands memories for your soulbinds to train against.

Name: Sacred Trials
Description:
Allows the capture of four more Shadowlands memories for training in the Path of Ascension.

Empowers some of your memories with accumulated anima, granting you access to their second trial.

Name: Continued Training
Description:
Empowers more of your captured memories, unlocking the rest of the Trials of Loyalty as well as the first of the Trials of Wisdom.

Their training on the Path has strengthened your soulbinds, increasing their health and damage.

Name: Teachings of Wisdom
Description: Your collected anima strengthens the remaining memories, granting access to the remaining Trials of Wisdom.

Name: Trials of Humility
Description:
Unlocks the final trial for all of your captured memories, the Trial of Humility. 

Your soulbinds reflect on their past trials and take lessons learned into these final trials, further increasing their health and damage.

Description: Expand the guest list, allowing you to invite a third guest to each Ember Court.

Name: The Professionals
Description: Hire five specialist staff who will help you foster the perfect atmosphere in each Ember Court.
